ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Directing that a Proclamation be Issued Proclaiming the Accession of a New Sovereign
PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION be issued proclaiming that His Royal Highness Prince Charles Philip Arthur George is, by the death of our late Sovereign, Charles the Third, by the Grace of God of the United Kingdom, Canada and His other Realms and Territories King, HEAD OF THE COMMONWEALTH, Defender of the Faith, to whom we acknowledge faith and allegiance.
